Package: rglPlotCustom
Type: Package
Title: rglPlot with cex (font size) support
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-02-28
Author: Roy Smith <roy.colton.smith@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Roy Smith <roy.colton.smith@gmail.com>
Description: rglPlot method from igraph package that is capable of using cex (font size) conditions for vertex labels.
				Passing the vertex.label.cex argument will alter the font size as a multiple of the base value.
				ex. vertex.label.cex=2 (font is double the base size). vertex.label.cex=0.5 (font is half the base size).
License: GPL
